---
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<Header />

<main>
  <section class="hero">
    <h1>About Terminus Maximus</h1>
    <p>
      Tacticus infographics, strategy resources, and guides created to help players
      make smarter decisions and progress more efficiently.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="about-card">
    <img
      src="/images/terminus-maximus.png"
      alt="Terminus Maximus"
      class="profile-image"
    />

    <div class="about-text">
      <h2>Who Am I?</h2>

      <p>
        I'm Terminus Maximus, a long-time Tacticus player focused on creating
        infographics and strategy resources for the community.
      </p>

      <p>
        What started as Reddit posts to help my guild has evolved into an official role as a Creator for Tacticus, working directly with Snowprint.
      </p>

    </div>

<section class="info-section">
  <h2>My Tacticus Experience</h2>

  <div class="game-entry">
    <h3>Guild Experience</h3>

    <ul>
      <li>Member of Bloody Rose: Main</li>
      <li>Guild Raid Rank: 1</li>
      <li>Guild War Rank: 1</li>
      <li>
        Guild Discord:
        <a
          href="https://discord.gg/bN269v34V"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
        >
          Join our Discord
        </a>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="game-entry">
    <h3>Roster Progress</h3>

    <ul>
      <li>Playing since October 2022</li>
      <li>
        View my roster:
        <a
          href="https://tacticusplanner.app/sharedRoster?username=TerminusMaximus&shareToken=4a64af58-a7ed-4a67-be6f-31a49b2f4c1b"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
        >
          Public Roster
        </a>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>



<section class="info-section">
  <h2>My Gaming Experience</h2>

  <div class="game-entry">
    <h3>Warhammer 40,000: Tacticus</h3>
    <p class="game-dates">October 2022 to Present</p>

    <ul>
      <li>Strategy guide creator and infographic designer</li>
      <li>Focus areas: Guild Raids, Legendary Release Events, Campaign Events, and progression optimization</li>
      <li>Active contributor to the Reddit and Discord communities</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="game-entry">
    <h3>Warhammer 40,000: Space Marine 2</h3>
    <p class="game-dates">December 2025 to Present</p>

    <ul>
      <li>Casual player</li>
      <li>Focus on Operations & Stratagems</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="game-entry">
    <h3>Gaming Background</h3>

    <ul>
      <li>Lifelong strategy and RPG gamer</li>
      <li>EverQuest player (1999 to 2004)</li>
      <li>Other interests include Warhammer 40,000 tabletop, Dungeons & Dragons, music, and reading sci fi</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

  <section class="info-section">
    <h2>Contact Me</h2>
    <p>
      Discord is my preferred platform for messages
    </p>

    <p>
      Discord: terminus_maximus<br>

      Reddit:
      <a
        href="https://www.reddit.com/user/terminus_maximus/"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
      >
        u/terminus_maximus
      </a><br>

      YouTube:
      <a
        href="https://www.youtube.com/@TerminusMaximus"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
      >
        @TerminusMaximus
      </a>
    </p>
  </section>
</main>

<Footer />

<style>
  :global(body) {
    background-color: #121212;
    color: #f5f5f5;
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    margin: 0;
  }

  main {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .hero {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .hero p {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    color: #cccccc;
  }

  .about-card,
  .info-section {
    background: #1e1e1e;
    border: 1px solid #333;
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .about-card {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 2rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .profile-image {
    max-width: 300px;
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    border-radius: 10px;
  }

  .about-text {
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 300px;
  }

  h2 {
    color: #d4af37;
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  p {
    color: #cccccc;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

    .info-section a {
    color: #f5f5f5;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .info-section a:hover {
    color: #d4af37;
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .gaming-list {
    color: #cccccc;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .gaming-list > li {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .gaming-list ul {
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }
</style>